PROBLEM :
Write a program that will read a full name of person and abbreviate the first, second or middle by their first letter except the last name.

HOW I HAVE IMPLEMENTED THIS?
First take one full name and split them by using split(" ") by using space " ".
Then store those words in an array.
Then For every word in an array except last index element,take the First letter by using charAt() function and store it in new string variable.
Then if we reach the last index,directly append the last element to the new string variable.
Then we get the required output.

TEST CASE 1 :
  INPUT :
    Enter the Full Name
    Gottipati Venkata Naga Pavan
  OUTPUT :
    G V N Pavan
    
    
TEST CASE 2 :
  INPUT :
    Enter the Full Name
    Gottipati Pavan
  OUTPUT :
    G Pavan
    
    
TEST CASE 3 :
  INPUT :
    Enter the Full Name
    Pavan
  OUTPUT :
    Pavan
    
    
TEST CASE 4:
  INPUT :      //no input
    Enter the Full Name
    
  OUTPUT :
  
